Replication: https://rollupjs.org/repl?version=0.52.1&

This example consists of three modules with re-exports, where the final output is:

```js
import { func } from 'chunk-dqkezhr8.js';

if (func) func();

export default obj;
```

instead of what should be:

```js
import { func, obj } from 'chunk-dqkezhr8.js';

if (func) func();

export default obj;
```

That is, the `obj` export is being dropped as an import name through the re-export referencing somehow.
